OL,3,CEnvironmentalists urge islanders to
OL,4,Crecycle Christmas waste
OL,6,FOne visitor to the La Collette
OL,7,Frecycling centre told ITV News: "We
OL,8,Fhad a car load, but we always recycle
OL,9,Fall our wrapping paper and cardboard -
OL,10,Fespecially after Christmas."
OL,12,FAnother said: "(The recycling centre)
OL,13,Fis packed. 2024 was the year climate
OL,14,Fchange fell off the agenda for a lot
OL,15,Fof people, but it's important always
OL,16,Fto recycle. Think of the planet."
OL,18,FNigel Jones, of the campaign group
OL,19,FJersey in Transition, believes there
OL,20,Fis much more work to be done to
OL,21,Fprevent excess waste.
